{"id:": "/div[1]", "tag": "div", "attributes": {"type": "article", "{http://www.w3.org/XML/1998/namespace}id": "MG-1686-02a_261", "resp": "wordpro"}, "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]", "tag": "head", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]/text()[1]", "text": "[Madrigaux]"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]", "tag": "bibl", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]", "tag": "title", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Mercure galant"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/text()[1]", "text": ", février 1686 (première partie) [tome 2], p. 261-263"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]", "tag": "p", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[2]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Je vous envoye un Madrigal, que M"}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[2]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[2]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "r"}], "attributes": {"rend": "sup"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[2]/text()[2]", "text": " Vignier a fait pour une Dame de la Religion Pretenduë Reformée, qui songeant à s’échaper du Royaume, luy demanda une Fuite de nostre Seigneur en Egypte, d’aprés le Poussin. Il accompagna ce present des Vers qui suivent."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Voicy les Fugitifs que vous me demandez,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": " Leur fuite n’est pas un mistere"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Qui puisse autoriser ce que vous voulez faire,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": "Ny vous faire esperer ce que vous attendez."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[5]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[5]/text()[1]", "text": "De sortir du Royaume, Iris, perdez l’envie,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[6]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[6]/text()[1]", "text": "Tous trois fuyoient la Mort, & vous fuiriez la Vie."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[3]", "tag": "p", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[4]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[4]/text()[1]", "text": "J’ay sceu que la Dame ne parle plus de se retirer, & que donnant tous ses soins à se faire instruire, elle se sert de ce Madrigal, pour engager ceux qu’elle voit encore dans l’aveuglement où elle estoit, à imiter son exemple. Les Conversions ont donné lieu à cet autre Madrigal, qu’on a tourné d’une maniere galante."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "La France sous LOUIS, prend des faces nouvelles,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": " Plus de Schisme, plus de Calvin ;"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": " Il n’est plus d’Heretique enfin,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": "Mais il est bien encor, Iris, des Infidelles."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}]}]}